select * from (
select CONSTANT_NAME AS CONSTANT_NAME ,'OWNER' as OWNER, 'P' AS SOURCE_TYPE FROM page
union
select SERVICE_NAME as CONSTANT_NAME, 'OWNER' AS OWNER , 'V' AS SOURCE_TYPE from virtual_domain
union
select CONSTANT_NAME AS CONSTANT_NAME ,'OWNER' AS OWNER, 'C' AS SOURCE_TYPE from css ) WHERE SOURCE_TYPE = :type
